{"tid":1930460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"AXA保險經紀確診！公司教瞞報！","createTime":"2020-03-17T14:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T01:55:49.000Z","uid":16686,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"648f95ef3157f674efcd1cfb0688c74c351f76db","tid":1930460,"uid":16686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:20:34.000Z","msg":"朋友代po<br />\n<br />\n當事人係AXA做agent，公司地址為利園一期。當事人管理層今日早晨會議向所有agent宣布，公司有人中肺炎，而確診者為第154宗個案外遊確診者，為AXA的保險agent。確診後，公司管理層叫呢個員工瞞報自己agent身分，叫員工報自己為家庭主婦，以免影響自己公司生意。而管理層也在會議中宣布，該位確診同事已被即時解僱。<br />\n<br />\n該位agent確診後，公司無任何消毒行為，亦無通知衛生處，只有確診者所屬的team被要求停工；但實際上公司人口密度非常高，一層已有幾百個座位。該agent確診後，其他員工照樣返工。每星期一至六，管理層都會召開大會，集合最少一百位agent於密封office開會，每次會議時長大概為一小時，實在罔顧員工安全。鄰近會議結束時，更告誡同事不要亂傳遙遠，否則會遭解僱。"},{"pid":"0d7ef253dd5e55cc365f929790c9425c7741edf5","tid":1930460,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:28:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d1a8ee90fddab7fd51e60195fc2bad96848c0d90","tid":1930460,"uid":249253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672275480bbf57fe0e424a4468311d6a16b013ed","tid":1930460,"uid":38572,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"AXA 叫人暪後再炒鳩人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19aac5d1bd8c3f8ca50663350408545df193d3c","tid":1930460,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db69c9c7ac4e2c5bef6142c45f20642d364edf6","tid":1930460,"uid":16686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:41:06.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"a3671c04a1757e477